    "reply_to_tweet_id": "reply_to_tweet_id_000011",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "text": "Nate, did you see what Jeff posted on Facebook? I don't know how to reply on there. Karen keeps saying just hit the little thumbs up but I want to say something."
